title: TotalEnergies hits pause on new Adani deal
description: TotalEnergies (TTE) has not yet signed a contract, announced last year, to extend its partnership with India's Adani to the production of green hydrogen, the chief executive of the French oil major said Wednesday.

title: Chinese savers stashed away $2.6 trillion last year but property crash will cool 'revenge spending'
description: Even for a famously frugal nation, Chinese people saved a lot last year. Stuck at home due to Covid restrictions, they socked away a record $2.6 trillion.
